Return a stacked ggplot barchart of processed emergences by recapture status

Source: R/summarise_wastd_data.R
ggplot_sighting_status_per_area_season_species.Rd

Facets: species

ggplot_sighting_status_per_area_season_species(data)

Arguments

data

The output of total_emergences_per_area_season_species, a summary of wastd_data.

Value

A ggplot2 figure
